    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College premises is very big, especially ground.",
          "name": "Samiksha Gautam",
          "course_tag_name": "MA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library of the vasanta college provide all the books related to different courses with 15 days issue of any two books with the issued library card .And they also provide the facility of e - library.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Low fees. Budget friendly.College surrounding. Its just located behind the River Ganges. The college has a great ambiance",
          "name": "Pragya Vatsa",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The colleage is good for professional and personal development",
          "name": "Aiswarya v",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Faculty is highly qualified and well trained with many more years of experience. Many publishers and authors are a part of the faculty of this college. They provide  good mentorship to the students and guide them well for ahead of their careers.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Ed"
        },
        {
          "text": "Too many clubs that enhance your personality and make you good person",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cleanliness and safety of the college which has to be Appreciated.",
          "name": "Anjali Kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Diversity of the college , despite being a girls college , the majority of the Populus belongs from different states",
          "name": "VAISHNAVI JAIN",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked the ambience of the college as it is placed in a quiet area",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is Fruit Chat Corner, Canteen, Library and And Playground. Also there is a Gym on the ground floor beside the auditorium. Auditorium is spacious and there is a culture of sitting on Eco-friendly mats in this auditorium.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Ed"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "They don't provide campus placement in their College",
          "name": "Punita Rao",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Irregularities in the timings of the classes and also the lack of punctuality in the faculty members. We wasted our hours in waiting for the teacher and suddenly we get to know that there is no class. Miscommunicated tudents missed their classes",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Ed"
        },
        {
          "text": "The management of college do not provide any clear information regarding the suitable scholarship that a student is eligible in offline mode,if asked they don't give any useful information.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College area like it is situated in back of markets,but on the upper side of namo ghat",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "One the main things of discomfort,is the location of college in which it is situated,as it in the outskirts of Varanasi",
          "name": "Aastha Vyahut",
          "course_tag_name": "MA"
        },
        {
          "text": "And if u opt for hostel,the fees of hostel is very much that 1 lakh for a academic year",
          "name": "Aastha Vyahut",
          "course_tag_name": "MA"
        },
        {
          "text": "They should increase their practical exposure to students",
          "name": "Punita Rao",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "They should increase their canteen area and provided healthy snacks",
          "name": "Punita Rao",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "No digital facility available regarding studies",
          "name": "Anjali Kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Medical Facility is not available in our college",
          "name": "Anjali Kumari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
